    "description": "Wabash National India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Surat location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Wabash National India:\nWabash National India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Wabash National India!",
